<h4 id="源码结构">源码结构</h4>
<ul>
  <li>ReactFiberBeginWork (“entering” a component)</li>
  <li>ReactFiberCompleteWork (“leaving” a component)</li>
  <li>ReactFiberCommitWork (flushing changes to DOM)</li>
  <li>ReactFiberScheduler (choosing next component to work on)</li>
  <li>ReactChildFiber (diffing insertions/deletions of children)
    <blockquote>
      <p>https://github.com/reactjs/reactjs.org/pull/745#issuecomment-377717600</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
</ul>

